data.description: This beautiful, well-maintained home is located minutes from downtown Grayson, Lawrenceville, and The Shoppes at Webb Gin. The house includes beautiful laminate floors, fresh interior paint, an open concept for entertaining, with vaulted ceilings in the family room. House is situated perfectly back from the street, boasting a beautiful brick front. Home includes a 4-camera security system with easy transition to new owner. New energy efficient windows. Home is move-in ready and SOLD AS IS.
